            + `created:desc` 

    + status (enum[string], optional)

        Can be used multiple times. The response will only contain Server matching the status

        + Members
            + `initializing` 
            + `starting` 
            + `running` 
            + `stopping` 
            + `off` 
            + `deleting` 
            + `rebuilding` 
            + `migrating` 
            + `unknown` 


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        A paged array of servers

    + Attributes (Servers Response)




