        The `action` key contains the `detach_volume` Action

    + Attributes (ActionResponse)


    + Body

            {"action":{"command":"detach_volume","error":{"code":"action_failed","message":"Action failed"},"finished":null,"id":13,"progress":0,"resources":[{"id":42,"type":"server"}],"started":"2016-01-30T23:50:00+00:00","status":"running"}}



## Volumes Actions Resize By Id [/volumes/{id}/actions/resize]

