## Volume1 (object)


### Properties
+ `created`: `2016-01-30T23:55:00+00:00` (string, required) - Point in time when the Resource was created (in ISO-8601 format)
+ `format`: `xfs` (string, required, nullable) - Filesystem of the Volume if formatted on creation, null if not formatted on creation
+ `id`: `42` (number, required) - ID of the Resource
+ `labels` (string, required) - User-defined labels (key-value pairs)
+ `linux_device`: `/dev/disk/by-id/scsi-0HC_Volume_4711` (string, required) - Device path on the file system for the Volume
+ `location` (Location16, required) - Location of the Volume. Volume can only be attached to Servers in the same Location.
+ `name`: `my-resource` (string, required) - Name of the Resource. Must be unique per Project.
+ `protection` (Protection, required) - Protection configuration for the Resource
+ `server`: `12` (number, required, nullable) - ID of the Server the Volume is attached to, null if it is not attached at all
+ `size`: `42` (number, required) - Size in GB of the Volume
+ `status` (enum[string], required) - Current status of the Volume
    + `creating`
    + `available`


## Location16 (object)
Location of the Volume. Volume can only be attached to Servers in the same Location.

### Properties
+ `city`: `Falkenstein` (string, required) - City the Location is closest to
+ `country`: `DE` (string, required) - ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 code of the country the Location resides in
+ `description`: `Falkenstein DC Park 1` (string, required) - Description of the Location
+ `id`: `1` (number, required) - ID of the Location
+ `latitude`: `50.47612` (number, required) - Latitude of the city closest to the Location
+ `longitude`: `12.370071` (number, required) - Longitude of the city closest to the Location
+ `name`: `fsn1` (string, required) - Unique identifier of the Location
+ `network_zone`: `eu-central` (string, required) - Name of network zone this Location resides in


## CreateVolumeRequest (object)


### Properties
+ `automount`: `false` (boolean, optional) - Auto-mount Volume after attach. `server` must be provided.
+ `format`: `xfs` (string, optional) - Format Volume after creation. One of: `xfs`, `ext4`
+ `labels`: `{"labelkey":"value"}` (object, optional) - User-defined labels (key-value pairs)
+ `location`: `nbg1` (string, optional) - Location to create the Volume in (can be omitted if Server is specified)
+ `name`: `databases-storage` (string, required) - Name of the volume
+ `server` (number, optional) - Server to which to attach the Volume once it's created (Volume will be created in the same Location as the server)
+ `size`: `42` (number, required) - Size of the Volume in GB


